node.text: Drake drops tonight, but I wrote this in August 2018 when Drake’s last album came out. It’s dope to see how my writing has progressed over the years. I’ve gotten SO much better. Like I would never post or write this nowadays. 2021 me wants to kick 2018 Kevin’s ass. Spit in his mouth a little.
